N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18ยง 225.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

When used in this Chapter unless otherwise expressly
stated: (a) Board shall mean the State

Board of Social Welfare. (b) Rules
shall mean the rules of the board as provided in this Chapter. (c) Executive director shall mean the
executive director of the board. (d) Department shall mean the State

Department of Social Services. Notes
